<!--

FEUER UND FLAMME
Theme 6 – Revamp, by silbrigthemes
    

"Feuer und Flamme sein" (ger., lit.: being fire and flame):
a figure of speech used to express being passionate about something

One column sidebar theme, with gradients.

RULES:

    1) Do not claim as your own.
    2) Do not steal (parts of) the code.
    3) Do not edit beyond recognition.
    4) Do not use as a base code.
    5) Do not delete or alter the credit.
    6) Please like / reblog if you’re using this theme.

If you have any questions or need help, feel free to contact me via
    »» silbrigthemes.tumblr.com/ask
    »» silbrigsupport.tumblr.com
        
Useful annotations have been made; a customization guide is linked in    the blog post.    

Shine bright for your passions, but don't burn yourself out!
    
Love, Julia
    
----------

Note:

    This work is protected by a creative commons
    Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International
